Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:48.08,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}愚かでいいのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:48.08,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}我可以懵懂無知吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:52.49,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}見渡す夢の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:52.49,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}眺望著夢想的痕跡
